
{center}
{subhead} NewsRog 1.8b{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

ShadowWorks Software announces the Version 1.8b update to NewsRog, the
most advanced newsreader available for the Amiga platform.  NewsRog has a
wealth of features for the power user, many of them unavailable in any
other newsreader on any platform.
{p} {p}
Version 1.8b includes 15 changes and improvements to version 1.8.
{p} {p}
For a full list of major changes in this version, as well as descriptions
of major NewsRog features and example screenshots, see the NewsRog preview
page at:
{p} {p}
{link http://www.frii.com/~srk/ShadowWorks/Preview/NR.html}http://www.frii.com/~srk/ShadowWorks/Preview/NR.html{end}
{p} {p}
The version 1.8b update is free to registered users and may be downloaded
from the "Updates" section of the above web page.
{p} {p}
PRICING AND AVAILABILITY
{p} {p}
NewsRog is priced at (US) $35 plus shipping and handling.  Orders
may be placed by telephone by calling:
{p} {p}
   (US) 1-303-659-4028
{p} {p}
Or online via major credit cards from either of the following pages:
{p} {p}
   {link http://www.questarproductions.com/NRorder.html}http://www.questarproductions.com/NRorder.html{end}    (unsecure)
{p} {p}
   https://www.dimensional.com/questar/NRorder.html  (secure)
{p} {p}
Free NewsRog updates may be downloaded from the Support web page.
{p} {p}
REQUIREMENTS
{p} {p}
NewsRog requires:
{p} {p}
   o  MUI 3.8 or later{p}
   o  8 Mb RAM & 8 Mb HD (more recommended){p}
   o  AmiTCP, Miami, or other compatible networking software{p}
   o  A 68020 or faster CPU (68040+ recommended)
{p} {p}
Only the Amiga version is available at this time.